## Complexity Analysis

| Operation                      | Time Complexity |
| ------------------------------ | --------------- |
| Calculate Minimum Contribution | O(n)            |
| Calculate Maximum Contribution | O(n)            |

**Total Time Complexity:** `O(n)`

**Space Complexity:** `O(n)`

Reason:

* Stack
* Left array
* Right array

